# PanelItems - endpoints de ejemplo

### Obtener todos los panel items
GET http://localhost:4000/api/panelitems
Accept: application/json

### Obtener panel item por id
GET http://localhost:4000/api/panelitem/1
Accept: application/json

### Crear panel item (ejemplo)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/panelitems
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "panelId": 1,
  "kind": "EXAM",
  "examId": 2,
  "required": true,
  "order": 1
}
# Items de panel API
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@authToken = {{authToken}}

## Rutas publicas

### Crear item de panel (publico)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/panelitem/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "panelId": 1,
  "kind": "EXAM",
  "examId": 2,
  "required": true,
  "order": 1,
  "notes": "Examen obligatorio",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Listar items de panel (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/panelitems/public
Accept: application/json

### Obtener item de panel por id (publico)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/panelitem/1/public
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar item de panel (publico)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/panelitem/1/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "required": false,
  "order": 2,
  "notes": "Se vuelve opcional",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar item de panel fisicamente (publico)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/panelitem/1/public

### Baja logica de item de panel (publico)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/panelitem/1/logic/public
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}

## Rutas protegidas (requieren token)

### Crear item de panel (con auth)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/panelitem
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "panelId": 2,
  "kind": "PARAMETER",
  "parameterId": 5,
  "required": true,
  "order": 1,
  "notes": "Incluye referencia",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Listar items de panel (con auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/panelitems
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Obtener item de panel por id (con auth)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/panelitem/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Actualizar item de panel (con auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/panelitem/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "required": true,
  "order": 3,
  "notes": "Reordenado en el panel",
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

### Eliminar item de panel fisicamente (con auth)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/panelitem/1
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Baja logica de item de panel (con auth)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/panelitem/1/logic
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "INACTIVE"
}
